Meet the professional boxing round timer! This app, simple and easy to use, is suitable for any type of training and competition preparation. Use the timer during boxing training, martial arts and wrestling classes, fitness, etc. 

Features:

- ability to create your own timers;
-Intuitive interface;
- Flexible settings of intervals, suitable not only for professionals, but also for beginners in sports;
- ready-made profiles for different sports;
- Signals of the beginning and end of rounds. 

Boxing timer is one of the best applications for amateur and professional boxing, MMA and any other martial arts and an excellent assistant for training at home.

